    [Bug fix] In some older cuda toolkits, eg. cuda 11.4, float to half conversion is not implicit. This was raised in [PR-57](<https://github.com/NVIDIA/cudnn-frontend/pull/57>). Thanks @drisspg for reporting this. A more correct fix has been implemented in this patch.

    [Enhancement] Accepting github [PR-55](<https://github.com/NVIDIA/cudnn-frontend/pull/55>). Thanks @r-barnes for the suggestion.
